{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "CJTHBQ5RJLPDZNZZRSC5BAI5O3PGLEKV",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041009005",
    "title": "裏表、ユウトウセイ",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日の放課後。トレーニングを始めるため、\r\nダイワスカーレットを迎えに行くと――",
            "enText": "After school. \nI came to pick up Daiwa Scarlet for training, when…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "pathId": -5248877235410932740,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "先生A",
            "enName": "Teacher A",
            "jpText": "朝からいろいろと頼んじゃって、ごめんなさいね。\r\nでも本当に助かったわ、ありがとう。",
            "enText": "I'm really sorry for asking you to do so many things since early \nthis morning. But you've really been a huge help, so thank you.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 187,
            "pathId": -6097613347144088386,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "そんな、このくらい大したことじゃありません。\r\n必要な時は、いつでも仰ってくださいね！",
            "enText": "Oh no, it's no big deal. \nPlease tell me whenever you need any help!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 176,
            "pathId": 8207230359439221833,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "それじゃ、失礼しまーす。",
            "enText": "Now if you'll excuse me, I'll be going now!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "pathId": 7674610418644032888,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……ふぅっ。朝からいろいろ頼まれごとの多い日だったわね……。\r\nさっさとトレーニングの準備に行かないと――",
            "enText": "…Phew. People have been asking me favors all day… \nI've got to start getting ready for training-",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 235,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "疲れた顔してるな",
                    "enText": "You look a bit tired.",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "疲れた顔してるね",
                    "enText": "You look a bit tired.",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 210,
                    "pathId": 7938562487785592493
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3850068749957033074
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -8227604499014195422
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3685205367282455355,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "ひゃあ！？　ト、トレーナー！？　びっくりさせないでよ！",
            "enText": "Hya!? <i>T</i>-Trainer!? Don't scare me like that!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 128,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": 744606353436329154
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -9192353809149669928
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4075702739579796805,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……ったく、わざわざ呼びに来たわけ？\r\n余計なお世話だっての！　今から行くとこだったんだから。",
            "enText": "…Sheesh, you went out your way to pick me up? I was about to \nstart heading there anyway. Mind your own business.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 247,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 1368509995251602607
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 2233851505967158470
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6593230189491617208,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……それと、別に疲れた顔なんてしてないから。\r\nアンタの気のせいよ、気のせい。",
            "enText": "…Also, I'm not tired at all. \nYou're just imagining things.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 220,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 1281900663672058627
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 7771391899677248900
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1791039770854729343,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "頼まれごとなんて日常茶飯事なんだから、どうってことないわ。",
            "enText": "Doing favors for people is part of my daily \nroutine so this is nothing to me.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 130,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "無理はしないようにな？",
                    "enText": "Don't overdo it, okay?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "無理はしないようにね？",
                    "enText": "Don't overdo it, okay?",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 6137579597392476332
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3637913153193749416,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "わかってるわよ。けどね、アタシは優等生なの。",
            "enText": "Yeah, yeah. I get it. Just so you know, I'm an honor student.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 142,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -4483330358487244094
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1627510973863928104,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "誰よりも頼りになって、誰の期待も裏切らない。\r\n生活態度も勉強も走りも、誰にも負けない1番のウマ娘。",
            "enText": "More relied on than anyone else, and never failing anyone's \nexpectations. The best horse girl in terms of lifestyle, \nacademics and racing: Number one.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 312,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -1307010834814640317
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -71050786040685190
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7658934376520999851,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "それがダイワスカーレットなの！\r\nこのくらいのこと、自分でどうにかするわ。",
            "enText": "That's what it means to be Daiwa Scarlet! \nI can handle something as small as this myself.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 177,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 140,
                    "pathId": 1961389118388349575
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5558349319266254088,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "私生活のことまで気にしてないで、\r\nアンタはトレーニングだけに集中して。",
            "enText": "Don't worry about my personal life and just focus on my training.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 157,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "でも、君を支えるって言っただろう？",
                    "enText": "I told you I'd support you, though?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "でも、貴方を支えるって言ったよね？",
                    "enText": "I told you I'd support you, though?",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 6622621979963721642
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1414718918377979277,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "そ、それはスカウトの時の話で……！\r\nそりゃあ、1番をとるためとは言ってたけど！",
            "enText": "That was all the way back when you scouted me…! \nWell… I did say I was going to be number one, but…!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 241,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 206,
                    "pathId": 8804567653191603235
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": 3137101588704911995
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -3037467495536670701
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2204021834449828770,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "だからって……\r\nこんなことまでアンタが気にする必要は……。",
            "enText": "But that… doesn't mean you have to concern \nyourself with something like this…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 9037530145735256653
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5497122039127673454
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1974133707266178560,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトA",
            "enName": "Classmate A",
            "jpText": "ダイワスカーレットさん！\r\nちょっといい？",
            "enText": "Daiwa Scarlet-san! Can I ask you something?",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6379900678727354216
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 701550614090882530,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "あっ……な、なーに？　どうかしたの？",
            "enText": "Ah… Y-yes? What is it?",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 96,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 2040521577847230463
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8596154917505194735
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -1126148730168655300
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9086431338606035051,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトA",
            "enName": "Classmate A",
            "jpText": "明日の調理実習の準備で、器具を用意しておかなきゃいけないの。\r\n悪いんだけど、手伝ってもらえないかなぁ。",
            "enText": "Actually, we need to get some appliances in place for tomorrow's \nhome-ec class… Sorry to bother you, but… I was wondering if \nyou could help us with that.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 214,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 163,
                    "pathId": -1337783804678118360
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 192,
                    "pathId": -8900336881416814105
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3473332934190903294,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "ええ、構わないわよ！\r\nすぐに行くから先に行っててくれる？",
            "enText": "Yeah, I don't mind! \nI'll be right there, so could you start without me?",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 132,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -7169261496095394452
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": 3862343829398440503
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 108801117603054838,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "クラスメイトA",
            "enName": "Classmate A",
            "jpText": "わっ、ありがと！　やっぱり頼りにしてよかった～！\r\nそれじゃ待ってるねっ。",
            "enText": "Wow, thanks! I knew I should have asked you! \nSee you at the storage room, then!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 156,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -450011669126825918
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": 2581887575475327743
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3993073582134293904,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……トレーナー、悪いけど先に行ってて。",
            "enText": "Trainer, sorry but you'll have to go without me.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "手伝うよ",
                    "enText": "I'll help you.",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -1262339871929293348
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -435499396035096108
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1771614615201930468,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "いい、アタシがやる。……別にアンタがどうこうじゃなくて、\r\n頼まれたことを他人任せにしたくないの。",
            "enText": "No, I don't need any help… It's got nothing to \ndo with you, but… I just don't want to rely on \nanyone else for something I got asked to do.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 276,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 233,
                    "pathId": 6635783951909450209
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 4929557020222609769
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 7175664411475306117
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7206475676382599395,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "それよりもほら、アンタは先にトレーニングの準備をしておいて！\r\nすぐに行くから、いいわね！？",
            "enText": "You should just focus on getting stuff ready for training! \nI'll be there soon, okay?",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 221,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 3778957244862397197
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1764365731505694338,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ダイワスカーレットに追い払われてしまった……。",
            "enText": "I got driven out by her…",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2482063145527073557
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -7909094408370822332
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1421486949806852887,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "それから30分後――",
            "enText": "30 minutes later.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -2358254081017129834
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2000672948872362292,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "はぁ……思ってたより時間がかかっちゃったわね。\r\nさっ、始めましょ。",
            "enText": "Phew… That sure took longer than I thought it would. \nAnyway, let's get started.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 216,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": -1729813222691705942
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5190647522335093339
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8686132550180475684,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……って、なによ。ジーッと見つめて……もしかして怒ってるの？\r\nまあ、待たせたのは悪かったけど。",
            "enText": "…Hey, what's with you? You've been staring… are you angry at \nme? Well, sorry for making you wait.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 290,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "1人で無理しないでくれ",
                    "enText": "Don't push yourself so hard.",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "1人で無理しないで",
                    "enText": "Don't push yourself so hard.",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": 371124014852290564
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -5362554324104707590
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3801499928174903114,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "べ、別にしてないわよ！\r\nこのくらいこなせなきゃ、1番ではいられないんだから！",
            "enText": "I can't stay number one if I can't even do something like that!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 177,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": 3075869786893846209
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 6765786074685098630
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 626273241506644884,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "トレーニングだって、遅れた分は必ず取り戻して――",
            "enText": "The same goes for my training. \nI'll just have to make up for how long I've been late-",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "もっと俺を頼ってくれ！",
                    "enText": "You've got to rely on me more!",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "もっと私を頼って！",
                    "enText": "You've got to rely on me more!",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 6117062125334055686
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8308015522379914458,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……っ。\r\nなによ……アタシが意地張ってるみたいな言い方しないで！",
            "enText": "What the heck… Don't make it sound \nlike I'm the one being stubborn!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 170,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -7503415428837744719
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 8515173417969437639
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2514589054876179961,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "それに……アンタのことは、\r\nトレーナーとしてなら……そ、それなりに……。",
            "enText": "Well… You're my trainer after all… \nIf that's the case, then…",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 229,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": -3812484228861038736
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -3858420150761068374
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1666846821684447649,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "――ああっ、もう！　なんか腹立つ！\r\nいいからもうトレーニング始めるわよ！",
            "enText": "Ughh, jeez! This is pissing me off! \nLet's just get this thing started already!",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 167,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -2136546278349002968
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -3093343737445823953
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 7431591349586990669
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3993862362048159368,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "1番にこだわるウマ娘、ダイワスカーレット。\r\n気難しい彼女に頼られるには、まだまだ先が長そうだ……。",
            "enText": "Daiwa Scarlet, the horse girl obsessed with being number one. It \nlooks like there's still a long way to go before she learns to \ntrust and depend on me.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 8935086975882928918
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5841941330319129331,
            "blockIdx": 33
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1669933655
}